            <pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 06:25:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1194772</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>電子收費系統「八達通」免費推出全新鈦金屬系列手機卡面，以配合 iPhone 15 Pro 和 Apple Watch Ultra 的推出。</p><p>八達通發公告指，為配合 iPhone 15 系列於香港開售，今日（22 日）推出四款鈦金屬系列手機卡面給予 iPhone 和 Apple Watch 用家免費下載。該卡面分別為「極祕．黑」、「極淨．白」、「極創．藍」、「極野．原」。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-694x439.png" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-694x439.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-768x486.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-694x439.png" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-694x439.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-768x486.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194786 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-13.54.21-387x580.png" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-13.54.21-387x580.png 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕截圖-2023-09-22-13.54.21.png 488w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" />（圖片來源：八達通手機 App）</p><p>不過，手機卡面亦適用於所有支援八達通的 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 新舊型號，不只限於新產品，只要打開八達通 App 內的卡面商店，下載「鈦」Pro 系列個性卡面即可。</p><p>當用家將八達通轉移到 iPhone 15 系列手機時，iOS 17 系統會幫助用家在設定「銀包」app 時，列出所有的已加載的卡，以方便用家轉移到新 iPhone。如在第一次設定時未能成功，只需要開啟「銀包」app，點擊右上角的「+」符號，選擇「之前的卡」，找「八達通」就可重新轉移。</p><p>另外，由即日起至 2023 年 10 月 31 日，新客戶加八達通入 iPhone 或 Apple Watch，再作一次消費交易，並於八達通網站登記優惠，合資格的客戶將於符合推廣要求的 7 天後收到八達通 App 通知領取迎新獎賞，在 11 月 10 日或之前就可到八達通 App 內的八達通卡面商店領取 $150 迎新獎賞及 1 張自選卡面。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.octopuscards.com/onlineform/promotion/general/registration/tc/step1.jsp?promotionRegRefCode=202309APO">octopuscards</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" framebord