n class="s1">1TB 13400 13300 13400 13300</span></p><p>iPhone 15 Pro Max</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">256GB 13600 13500 13700 13500</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">512GB 15000 14800 15100 14800</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">1TB 16700 16100 16200 16300</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">iPhone 15 Pro 收購價與原價的差額相對較低，128GB, 256GB 只有約 400~500 元的利潤，再上的 512GB, 1TB 亦只有 500~600 元利潤。</span></p><p>除了先達廣場內部，周圍都有不少收機檔口，但現場所見大部份放機者都會入商場才放機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-scaled.jpeg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194751" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-1200x900.jpeg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-1536x1152.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_3945-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
